snippet.title: Swatantrya Veer Savarkar | Trailer | 22nd March | Randeep Hooda | Ankita Lokhande | Amit Sial
snippet.description:
The British termed him the most dangerous man!
Indian revolutionaries revered him as "Veer"!
Yet, he was Unsung, Unhonoured, Unacknowledged & Unheard!
This 22nd March IN CINEMAS, HISTORY WILL BE REWRITTEN!
Witness the epic life of #SwantatryaVeerSavarkar & the Untold Saga of the Indian Armed Revolution.
#SwatantryaVeerSavarkarTrailer
#VeerSavarkarOn22March
#WhoKilledHisStory

A Film By Randeep Hooda
Produced By - Zee Studios, Anand Pandit, Sandeep Singh, Yogesh Rahar and Randeep Hooda
Story, Screenplay & Dialogue By - Utkarsh Naithani and Randeep Hooda
Co-Producer - Roopa Pandit, Sam Khan, Panchali Chakraverty, Anwar Ali
Associate Producers - Zafar Mehdi, Rahul V. Dubey and Sonu Kuntal

snippet.title: GOAT BLOOD FRY | Traditional Goat Blood Recipe Cooking In Village | Goat Blood Gravy with Intestine
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook our village's traditional goat blood recipe by making blood gravy and blood fry. We call this recipe as "Raththa Koottu" and "Raththa Poriyal". We add some goat internal parts to goat blood gravy, such as the liver, lungs, and intestine.

Finally, we enjoy the food with our favourite muttun curry! The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: Manjummel Boys ft. Guna Caves Mystery 🦇 😈 😱 | Madan Gowri | Tamil | MG
snippet.description:
In this video, Madan Gowri speaks about the recently released Malayalam blockbuster movie, Manjummel Boys, and the real incident in which the movie was inspired and made. He says that a gang of 11 boys from Kerala have travelled to Tamil Nadu's Kodaikanal for a trip. As a part of the trip, those boys went to Guna Caves, which are located in Kodaikanal, got trapped in the caves, and were finally rescued from there. This Manjummel Boys movie is based on this real-life incident. Guna Cave was named after the Guna movie, in which Kamal Hassan was the protagonist.

snippet.title: Mrs. Nita Ambani's Performance to Vishwambhari Stuti For Anant & Radhika's Prewedding Celebration
snippet.description:
Celebrating tradition and invoking the divine, Mrs. Nita Ambani presents a stirring performance to the Vishwambhari Stuti, a sacred hymn dedicated to Maa Ambe, the embodiment of power and strength. She has been hearing this hymn since her childhood during every Navratri. Tonight, as she performs with grace and devotion, she seeks Maa Ambe's blessings for Anant and Radhika's journey of togetherness. She also dedicates her performance to her granddaughters, Aadiya Shakti and Veda, and to all young girls, who are a symbol of feminine energy. 

Credits:
Music Directors/Composer: Ajay-Atul
Singer: Shreya Ghoshal
Director of Choreography: Vaibhavi Merchant
Mrs. Nita Ambani Costume: Manish Malhotra
Dancers' Costume: Ashley Rebello
Director of Photography: Anil Mehta

#AnantRadhika
#ARPreWeddingCelebrations #NitaMukeshAmbaniCulturalCentre
#SwadeshOnline

snippet.title: इस बीमारी से बढ़ा Anant Ambani का Weight, 19 साल की उम्र में 208 किलो हो गया था वजन
snippet.description:
मुकेश अंबानी और नीता अंबानी के बेटे अनंत अंबानी जल्द ही वीरेन मर्चेंट की बेटी राधिका मर्चेंट इस समय सुर्ख़ियों में हैं. बॉलीवुड से लेकर उद्योग इंडस्ट्री के सभी बड़े चेहरे उनके प्री-वेडिंग सेलिब्रेशन में शामिल हो रहे हैं. 2017 में अपने एक इंटरव्यू में अनंत अंबानी की मां नीता अंबानी ने बताया था कि उनका बेटा गंभीर अस्थमा से पीड़ित था, इसलिए उन्हें उसे बहुत सारे स्टेरॉयड पर रखना पड़ा, परिणाम स्वरूप अनंत का वजन फिर से बढ़ गया था.

snippet.title: Thankamani | Trailer | Dileep | Ratheesh Reghunandan | Super Good Films | Saina Music | Iffaar Media
snippet.description:
Thankamani is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language crime thriller film written and directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan and Produced by R B Choudhry under the banner of Super good films in association with Iffaar Media Raaffi Mathirra. The film stars Dileep and is based on a real-life incident that occurred in Thankamany in October 1986. Thankamani Music Rights has been acquired by Saina Music.

Written & Directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan
Produced by  RB Choudary , Raaffi Mathirra
D.O.P Manoj Pillai
Editor Shyam Sasidharan
Music William Francis
Executive Producer Sujit J Nair
Sound Design Ganesh Marar-Sreejesh Nair (Mixing)
Lyrics B T Anil Kumar
Art Director Manu Jagadh
Makeup Roshan
Costume Designer Arun Manohar
Stunts Rajasekhar, Supreme Sundar, Mafia Sasi, Stun Shiva
Project Designers Sajith Krishna, Ashokan AMrutha
Production Controller Mohan (Amritha)
Project Head Sumith B P
Asso. Directors Abhijith PR, Jophin Vargheese
Colorist Liju Prabhakar
VFX Eggwhite
Stills Shalu Peyad
Design Adsofads
Marketing & Distribution Dream Big Films

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! SUPERB FODEN BRACE INSPIRES CITY TO DERBY TRIUMPH | Man City 3-1 Man United
snippet.description:
Phil Foden scored two stunning goals as City recovered from a goal down to beat Manchester United 3-1.

City had fallen behind to a thunderous Marcus Rashford goal on eight minutes - against the run of play - and spent the next 50 minutes or so trying to find a way past a resolute United back-line.

But Foden levelled on 56 minutes with a screamer into the top corner from 20 yards, then scored a delightful second ten minutes from the end of normal time.

Erling Haaland wrapped up victory with a clinical finish following excellent work by Rodrigo to make it 3-1 in added time as the Blues moved within a point of leaders Liverpool.

snippet.title: #Exclusive | Anant Ambani And Rahul Kanwal Take a Tour of Vantara Kingdom Elephant Kitchen
snippet.description:
#anantambani #rahulkanwal #anantambaniengagement #mukeshambani #vantara #RadhikaMerchant #NitaAmbani 
Step into the fascinating world of Vantara Kingdom's Elephant Kitchen with Rahul Kanwal, Executive Director of Business Today, and Anant Ambani, Director of Reliance Industries Limited, in a special edition of 'Jab We Met'. Embark on an exclusive tour as Anant Ambani and Rahul Kanwal explore the intricacies of the Elephant Kitchen, where the majestic residents of Vantara Kingdom are nourished. Witness firsthand as Rahul Kanwal delves into the unique culinary offerings for the elephants, discovering surprising treats that are not only savored by these gentle giants but also enjoyed by humans. From tasting delectable ladoos to refreshing watermelon juice, indulging in wholesome khichdi, and savoring popcorn treats meant for the elephants, Rahul Kanwal immerses himself in the culinary delights of Vantara Kingdom's Elephant Kitchen. Experience the joy of this extraordinary encounter as Anant Ambani and Rahul Kanwal unravel the secrets of this special sanctuary.

Khumar Episode 30 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 2nd March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

Let’s see how to make healthy vegetable ghavan and chutney today. My daughter has specially asked me to make something light and full of veggies for breakfast. So, here I am with the recipe. Now a days, kids are cauntious what they eat specially during exam period. So in a way, this will helpful to you too. This is a very easy and simple recipe. As it has lot many veggies, it is healthy too!! This recipe doesn’t need lot many ingredients. You can make it from very few basic ingredients those are readily available in your kitchen. It looks nice and tempting and tastes just awesome. 

Ingredients:
Ghavan
• 4~5 tbsp Rice flour
• Salt to taste
• Water as needed
• Finely chopped Spinach
• Grated Carrot
• 1/2 Lemon juice
• Oil 
Chutney
• 1 tbsp roasted Chana dal
• 4~5 grated fresh Coconut
• Coriander leaves
• 2~3 Green chilies
• 1 small piece of Ginger
• Salt to taste
• Sugar to taste
• Water as needed
• 1/2 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Mustard seeds
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• A pinch of Hing
• Curry leaves

Method:
Ghavan
• Mix rice flour and salt well together and add a little water at a time to make runny batter. 
• Wash spinach and carrot really good and grate the carrot. 
• Chop the spinach finely. 
• You can add veggies of your choice like finely chopped onion, capsicum or tomato etc. 
• Add the veggies into the batter and add lemon juice. 
• Mix everything well together and batter for ghavan is ready. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and grease it well with oil. 
• Mix the batter well once and make ghavan. Start pouring the batter along the edge of the pan and
  finish off at the center. 
• Cover and cook the ghavan for about a minute. 
• Remove the lid and when lower side is roasted well, flip the ghavan over. 
• Roast well from other side too. 
• When the ghavan is roasted well from both sides, talk it off on a wore rack. Ghavan is ready. 
• Serve it with chutney.  
Chutney
• Blend roasted chana dal, fresh coconut, coriander leaves, green chilies, ginger, salt and sugar well 
  together dry first. Avoid use of water while blending now. 
• Add water and blend it well again. 
• Transfer the chutney into a bowl. 
• Heat up oil in a pan and add mustard seeds. 
• When mustard pop up turn on the gas and add cumin seeds, hing and curry leaves. 
• Mix well and add the tadka into the chutney. 
• Mix well and chutney is ready.

snippet.title: പുതിയ വീട്ടിലെ ധ്വനി മോൾടെ വിശേഷങ്ങൾ | Dwani's Formula Milk Experience | MRIDVA
snippet.description:
🌟 Welcome to Mridva Vlogs! 🌟
In today's heartwarming episode, we delve deep into our baby's night time routine, highlighting the pivotal role that Aptamil plays in ensuring our little one gets the best start in life. 🍼 As new parents, finding the perfect formula milk was a journey filled with learning and love. Our chosen infant formula milk has been a cornerstone in our nightly routine, providing not just nourishment but peace of mind.
👶 Why Aptamil Gold Stage 1? Well, as we navigated the challenges of colic in infants and the quest for the best formula milk, it stood out for its commitment to infant nutrition and infant immunity. The transition to formula milk for newborns was made smoother with its advanced formulation, designed to meet the nutritional needs of infants in the most wholesome way possible.
In tonight's vlog, we not only share our soothing bedtime ritual but also how Formula Milk powder, specifically Aptamil Gold Stage 1, seamlessly integrates into our routine. This lactose-free formula milk (a blessing for sensitive little tummies) and infant formula powder have supported our baby's growth and development beautifully, echoing the principles of nutrition pediatrics.
📖 From dimming the lights to wrapping up in snuggly blankets and embarking on fairy-tale adventures before bedtime, every step is a step towards growth and bonding. This formula milk  has been with us every step of the way, ensuring our baby's dietary needs are met with the highest standard of care.
💡 Whether you're a new parent grappling with the vast world of formula milk or seeking insights on infant nutrition, join us as we share our personal experiences with it. It's more than just a feeding solution; it's our trust in a brand that values the health and happiness of our most precious ones.
Remember, every child's needs are unique, and it's essential to consult with a healthcare provider to choose the best infant formula milk for your baby.
👉 Don't forget to LIKE, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more insights into our family's journey and tips on parenting, nutrition, and well-being. Drop your questions and experiences in the comments below—we love hearing from you!
#AptamilGoldStage1 #FormulaMilk #InfantNutrition #InfantImmunity #BestFormulaMilk #ParentingTips

snippet.title: Gaami Trailer | Vishwak Sen | Chandini Chowdary | Vidyadhar Kagita | UV Creations
snippet.description:
Gaami Trailer On UV Creations.

#Gaami chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive Aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare condition- ‘an inability to experience any human touch’.  But this adventure for cure would be fulfilled, only when he can confront and conquer his destiny that becomes intertwined with two other characters.

#GaamiTrailer #GaamiMovie #VishwakSen #ChandiniChowdary #VidyadharKagita #MGAbhinaya #MohammadSamad #NareshKumaran #GaamiTeluguMovie 

Movie details:-

Cast:- Vishwak sen, Chandini Chowdary, M G Abhinaya, Mohammad Samad, Harika Pedada, Dayanand Reddy, Shanthi Rao, Mayank Parakh, John Kottoly, Bomma Sreedhar, Rajnish Sharma, sharath kumar N, Shankar Mahanthi, Aumkar Kotamraju, KLK Mani, Sanjay Ratha, K R Unnikrishnan, B Venkat Raman Rao, Rajiv kumar, Mahija, Ram

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4023 | 4 Mar 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4023: Popatlal Akela Rahega
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal experiences a surreal moment as he hallucinates a version of himself, engaging in a conversation about his marriage concerns. Later, Popatlal envisions a celebration of his birthday where everyone wishes for his speedy marriage. Fueled by this hopeful imagination, he resolves to avoid meeting anyone on his birthday.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4023, 4 Mar 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Anant Ambani Crazy Diljit Dosanjh Performance, Srk folded his hands, Diljit Dosanjh energetic
snippet.description:

Witness an electrifying performance by the talented Diljit Dosanjh at the Anant Ambani Crazy Event, where he leaves everyone mesmerized with his high-energy performance. Watch as Bollywood superstar Shah Rukh Khan folds his hands in respect, acknowledging Diljit's unbeatable energy on stage. This video captures the essence of the unforgettable night that had the audience on their feet, cheering for more. Get ready to be amazed by the dynamic duo and experience the magic they create together. Don't miss out on this epic performance that showcases the best of Diljit Dosanjh and the charisma of Anant Ambani.

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 29 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 1st March 2024 - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 29 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 1st March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa

Minsa Malik as Laiba

snippet.title: किस से Impress होके Bhide ने किया ये ऐलान? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 1 Mar 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide, impressed by Tapu, decides to give him a gift but in return, gets pranked by him. Bhide informs everybody in the society to get ready for the upcoming census as two officers are scheduled to visit the society on the next day.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 541
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Anant Ambani's Exclusive Interview: Family, Vision, And Marriage Plans Revealed On 'Jab We Met'
snippet.description:
#anantambani #rahulkanwal #anantambaniengagement #mukeshambani #vantara 
Ahead of his pre-wedding celebrations, Anant Ambani interacted exclusively with Business Today's Executive Director, Rahul Kanwal on the special episode of 'Jab We Met'. During the conversation, he opened up about his family, his vision of the rescue and rehabilitation center Vantara, and his marriage with Radhika Merchant.  Anant also spoke up about being an Ambani and whether he feels pressure to live up to his grandfather Dhirubai Ambani and father Mukesh Ambani's legacy. Anant Ambani is set to tie the knot with Radhika Merchant in July this year. Also, Anant opened up on why he chose Gujarat's Jamnagar as the venue for pre-wedding festivities. Ahead of the same, the families would be hosting a three-day gala affair in Jamnagar with Bollywood celebs, sports personalities, and business leaders in attendance. Watch the mega exclusive interview here.
-----------------------
Thank You for watching! Do not forget to Like | Comment | Share 
-----------------------

snippet.title: SCAM - Every Teenager Story | Family Show | Episode 1 | MyMissAnand
snippet.description:
Online video games use various techniques to keep users engaged and encourage them to play more. They capture our senses by hypnotising and creating an environment with vibrant lights, captivating sounds, and a layout designed to keep us exploring. Online game apps utilise tactics of visuals, notifications, and personalised offers to keep users hooked. You may win a couple of times, but remember the game always win! 

So, today's video is all about how you can stuck in such manipulative situations.

Do comment and tell if you or your family member faced similar situation.

Do share and like the video with your family and friends.
Do Subscribe to my channel.

NEW UPLOADS every FRIDAY @2:00 PM.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4022: Popatlal Ka Janam Din
--------------------------------------------------------
Anjali decides to prank her friends and presents them with a cake made with Okra. Gokuldham residents prepare to celebrate Popatlal's birthday together. Popatlal takes a leave from work to celebrate his birthday. He returns home and eagerly waits for Tapu Sena to surprise him. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4022, 2 Mar 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Last Episode 122 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - 3rd March 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Last Episode 122 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 3rd March 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Will Urooj’s true identity pose a threat to her relationship with Salman?

Written By: Sajjad Haider Zaidi & Abu Rashid

snippet.title: Clash off into Space! (Clash of Clans March Season Challenges)
snippet.description:
This month Clash blasts off to outer space. Whether you're landing on an alien world or landing a 3-Star attack, these space-themed Skins and Challenges are out of this world!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/
